                     <interp inst="t18440101-472-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> stealing 5 handkerchiefs, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18440101-name-553" type="victimName">
