                        <interp inst="t18440101-name-558" type="given" value="WILLIAM HENRY"></interp>WILLIAM HENRY MILLS</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This is one of my handkerchiefs, and one I lost that evening—he might have had it an hour or an hour and a half.</p>
